Summary: TRIANGLE LIGHTS MOVING THROUGH THE AIR
divs: Sighting DetailsI WAS STANDING OUTSIDE WITH MY BOYFRIEND AND HE SAID WHAT THE HECK IS THAT. I TURNED AROUND AND SAW 3 STEADY DULL LIGHTS MOVING THROUGH THE AIR QUICKER THAN ANY PLANE COULD FLY. WE WATCHED IT FOR 3 MINUTES UNTIL IT FLEW INTO CLOUD COVER AND NEVER SAW IT COME OUT THE OTHER SIDE. FREAKED US OUT.
